sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant P as Pipeline
    participant G as Guardrails
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant AI as LLM (Claude/GPT)
    participant T as Tool Registry
    participant V as Validator

    U->>P: generate("Add a pricing section<br/>with 3 plan cards")
    P->>G: validateInput(prompt)
    G-->>P: allowed: true, risk: none

    P->>O: generate(request)
    Note over O: Build system prompt<br/>with schema context

    O->>AI: messages + tools
    AI-->>O: tool_call: inspect_tree({})
    O->>T: execute("inspect_tree", {})
    T-->>O: {tree: ..., nodeCount: 5}
    O->>AI: tool result

    AI-->>O: tool_call: lookup_schema("Card")
    O->>T: execute("lookup_schema", {type: "Card"})
    T-->>O: {found: true, schema: ...}
    O->>AI: tool result

    AI-->>O: JSON response with 4 changes<br/>(1 Grid + 3 Cards)

    O-->>P: GenerationResult

    P->>V: validateChanges(changes, schema)
    Note over V: Layer 1: Schema ✓<br/>Layer 2: Structure ✓<br/>Layer 3: Safety ✓<br/>Layer 4: Checksum ✓
    V-->>P: valid: true

    P->>P: applyChanges(tree, changes)
    P-->>U: updated tree + explanation
